::KItKat::

She looked at the monitor.  She was going to give Land Mine a 
warriors burial when the maximals had left.  She thought, it's the 
lest she could do for her friend.  She opened her 
link,"Terrorsaur...as soon as they leave, could," she cleared her 
throat,"could you get Land Mine's body for me."

She looked at her desk. She whispered,"Phobia, you have heard me 
before, please tell me I did the right thing. please"  She lowered 
her head on the desk and cried.
